    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable work car or budget-friendly option for a first-time driver. While the engine starts reliably and the car is fully functional for daily commuting, there are visible signs of wear including some noticeable exterior scratches and minor dings. The interior shows age with some staining on the upholstery and wear on the touchpoints. Mechanically, it runs well but may require some upcoming routine maintenance to keep it in peak shape. It is a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price tag.",
